      <string>Apply</string>
     </property>
     <property name="toolTip">
      <string>Run HD-BET on the DWI's mean b0 image. Requires kwneuro[hdbet] (install via KWNeuroEnvironment). HD-BET uses a deep-learning model that benefits from a CUDA GPU — on CPU it still runs but takes longer. Result is a labelmap volume named `{dwi_name}_brainmask`.</string>
